Let us only change the kvstore_device

If we want to get a global information. override the Init Function https://github.com/dmlc/mxnet/blob/master/src/kvstore/kvstore_local.h#L31 

``` c++
void Init(const std::vector<int>& keys,
             const std::vector<NDArray>& values) override {
    // call kvstore local init 
    KVStoreLocal::Init(keys, values);
   // add the strategy here. for example, assign each key to context. You can get size from values[i].shape().Size()
}
```

