1. In the mainland of China, OneDrive and Dropbox are unstable and slow. Actually, this archive is also a compiler. Someone has reported the Nov 2013 CTP patch cannot be installed successfully, so I packed the files on my computer and uploaded. I will learn how to use github's release service and upload it. Maybe I should also provide the MD5 of the zip file.
